Description: Rare black Gibson Les Paul Historic Custom Shop Plush Burgundy lined case in excellent clean vintage condition. Gold Latches and Vintage style handle work perfect. This was one of the first rare cases ever to come out of the Gibson Custom Shop when they separated from the regular Gibson Factory. Outside of the case is a alligator type material that is very durable. This case was designed for Gibson's best guitars. The Vintage Gibson is really clean ! If your Gibson Les Paul Guitar is newer or vintage, it will be living the life in this awesome rare Gibson Case! Super nice case.
